body_html:
Hi all, I had a chance to look into this. The issue is that dilated depthwise convolution isn't yet supported. The contrib/quantize rewrite supports this at HEAD but TOCO/TFLite doesn't have the inference transformations and quantized dilated depthwise convolution kernels implemented. This is something I am trying to complete soon so will keep you posted.

Thanks for your patience!
